videos.headline: Indiana RB sails over the goal line for TD
videos.description: Indiana RB Stevie Scott III flies over the pile to capitalize first for the Hoosiers.

videos.headline: Patterson finds Jackson downfield for huge 50-yard gain
videos.description: Shea Patterson lets it rip downfield and finds Giles Jackson wide open on the sideline for a big Wolverines gain.

videos.headline: Patterson finds Bell in the corner for TD
videos.description: Shea Patterson executes perfectly and finds his WR, Ronnie Bell, wide open in the corner for a short TD.

videos.headline: Ramsey keeps it for Hoosiers TD
videos.description: Peyton Ramsey gets a little bit of help from his team as he gets dragged into the end zone for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Peoples-Jones lays out for a 17-yard TD
videos.description: Donovan Peoples-Jones makes an incredible catch in coverage as he lays out for a 17-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Patterson lofts pass to Collins for 24-yard TD
videos.description: Shea Patterson puts it up for Nico Collins in the end zone and Collins comes away with the touchdown and the lead for Michigan.

videos.headline: Patterson finds Collins again for 76-yard TD
videos.description: Nico Collins catches a pass from Shea Patterson and takes off for a 76-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Collins shows off his ups for TD
videos.description: Shea Patterson fires a dart and Nico Collins makes the grab to extend Michigan's lead 39-14.
